.TH "set_sgttyb" 9 "set_sgttyb" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
set_sgttyb \- set legacy terminal values
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" set_sgttyb
.BI "(struct tty_struct *tty "  ","
.BI "struct sgttyb __user *sgttyb "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "tty" 12
tty structure
.IP "sgttyb" 12
pointer to old style terminal structure

Updates a terminal from the legacy BSD style terminal information
structure.

Locking: termios_rwsem
